r\n[/av_one_third][av_one_third min_height=\'\' vertical_alignment=\'\' space=\'\' custom_margin=\'\' margin=\'0px\' padding=\'0px\' border=\'\' border_color=\'\' radius=\'0px\' background_color=\'\' src=\'\' background_position=\'top left\' background_repeat=\'no-repeat\' animation=\'\' mobile_display=\'\']\r\n\r\n[av_icon_box position=\'left_content\' icon_style=\'\' boxed=\'av-no-box\' icon=\'ue80b\' font=\'entypo-fontello\' title=\'Consultant\' link=\'\' linktarget=\'\' linkelement=\'\' font_color=\'\' custom_title=\'\' custom_content=\'\' color=\'\' custom_bg=\'\' custom_font=\'\' custom_border=\'\' admin_preview_bg=\'\']\r\nConsulting experience for 12 years. Leader in branding, ROI, determining KPIs, SEM, and key concepts. Streamlines look for clients and brands alike. Forecasts trends and creates Google Ads/Facebook Ads/Twitter Ads with measurable success rates.\r\n[/av_icon_box]\r\n\r\n[/av_one_third][av_one_third min_height=\'\' vertical_alignment=\'\' space=\'\' custom_margin=\'\' margin=\'0px\' padding=\'0px\' border=\'\' border_color=\'\' radius=\'0px\' background_color=\'\' src=\'\' background_position=\'top left\' background_repeat=\'no-repeat\' animation=\'\' mobile_display=\'\']\r\n\r\n[av_icon_box position=\'left_content\' icon_style=\'\' boxed=\'av-no-box\' icon=\'ue853\' font=\'entypo-fontello\' title=\'Blogger\' link=\'\' linktarget=\'\' linkelement=\'\' font_color=\'\' custom_title=\'\' custom_content=\'\' color=\'\' custom_bg=\'\' custom_font=\'\' custom_border=\'\' admin_preview_bg=\'\']\r\nContent is Queen. Creative blogger with voice and tone matching skills, SEO/keywords, categories, alt tags, metadata, and various linking, affiliate work, including curation and original content.\r\n[/av_icon_box]\r\n\r\n[/av_one_third][av_one_third first]\r\n\r\n[av_icon_box position=\'left_content\' icon_style=\'\' boxed=\'av-no-box\' icon=\'ue83a\' font=\'entypo-fontello\' title=\'Web Producer\' link=\'\' linktarget=\'\' linkelement=\'\' font_color=\'\'